      { title: "Crypto Casinos", text: "Play with Bitcoin, Ethereum, and more. Anonymous gambling with instant withdrawals.", icon: "₿" },
      { title: "Poker Rooms", text: "Join the best online poker rooms. Tournaments, cash games, and freerolls with huge prize pools.", icon: "🃏" },
      { title: "Money Making", text: "Legitimate ways to earn money online. Side hustles, passive income, and money-making strategies.", icon: "💵" },
